---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Press & Media - The Wandering Lantern
---

<div class="container">
    <section id="press">
        <h2>Press & Media</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;">
            Welcome to our press room. Find press releases, media assets, and information about The Wandering Lantern.
        </p>

        <!-- Press Kit Download Section -->
        <div class="press-kit-section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(122, 139, 111, 0.08) 0%, rgba(139, 111, 71, 0.08) 100%); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2.5rem 2rem; text-align: center; margin: 3rem auto; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.2); max-width: 700px;">
            <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Media Kit</h3>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">High-resolution logos, photos, and brand information for media use.</p>
            <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 1rem;">
                <a href="#" class="cta-button" style="font-size: 0.95rem; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;">Download Press Kit</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Store Information -->
        <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(90, 75, 60, 0.1); margin: 3rem 0;">
            <h3 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Store Information</h3>
            <div style="max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto;">
                <p><strong>Official Name:</strong> The Wandering Lantern</p>
                <p><strong>Tagline:</strong> "Follow the light, find the wonder"</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> 15729 Madison Ave, Lakewood, OH 44107</p>
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (216) 999-4462</p>
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> thewanderinglanterncle@gmail.com</p>
                <p><strong>Website:</strong> thewanderinglantern.com</p>
                <p><strong>Social Media:</strong><br>
                   Instagram: @thewanderinglanterncle<br>
                   Facebook: @thewanderinglantern
                </p>
                <p><strong>Hours:</strong><br>
                   Tuesday - Saturday: 12 PM - 8 PM<br>
                   Sunday - Monday: Closed
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Boilerplate -->
        <div style="background: var(--parchment); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; margin: 3rem 0; border-left: 4px solid var(--aged-gold);">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">About The Wandering Lantern (Boilerplate)</h3>
            <p style="font-style: italic; line-height: 1.8;">
                The Wandering Lantern is Cleveland's first dedicated children's bookstore, offering a curated selection
                of picture books, middle grade novels, young adult fiction, and educational materials. Founded by Emily
                Mitchell and Michael Plant, the store serves as a community hub for families seeking quality children's
                literature and literary programming. Located in Lakewood's vibrant Madison Avenue district, The Wandering
                Lantern hosts regular storytimes, author events, and seasonal celebrations designed to spark imagination
                and foster a lifelong love of reading.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Press Releases -->
        <h3 style="margin-top: 4rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: center;">Press Releases</h3>
        {% if collections.press.length > 0 %}
        <div class="press-grid" style="display: grid; gap: 2rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
            {% for article in collections.press %}
            <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(90, 75, 60, 0.1);">
                <h4 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.3rem;">
                    <a href="{{ article.url }}" style="color: var(--deep-brown); text-decoration: none;">{{ article.data.title }}</a>
                </h4>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--warm-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    {{ article.data.date | date('MMMM D, YYYY') }}
                </p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">{{ article.data.excerpt }}</p>
                <a href="{{ article.url }}" style="color: var(--aged-gold); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
                    Read Full Release â†’
                </a>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% else %}
        <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--warm-brown);">No press releases available at this time.</p>
        {% endif %}

        <!-- Media Contact -->
        <div style="margin-top: 4rem; padding: 2rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(122, 139, 111, 0.08) 0%, rgba(139, 111, 71, 0.08) 100%); border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">Media Inquiries</h3>
            <p>For interview requests, high-resolution images, or additional information, please contact:</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                <strong>Emily Mitchell</strong><br>
                <a href="mailto:thewanderinglanterncle@gmail.com" style="color: var(--aged-gold);">thewanderinglanterncle@gmail.com</a><br>
                (216) 999-4462
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
